description: PONY Make up - Instagram Makeup-Summer daily look포니 메이크업 - 인스타 메이크업-썸머 데일리 룩Hi guys! It's pony!Today's look is from my Instagram photo i posted few days agoSo I am planning to make this series of "Instagram makeup tutorial" based on  the most requested look from my instagram. I'm going to show you the exact same makeup tools, products and techniques i used for that look.So, from now on, if you find a look on my instagram you wish me to make a tutorial, please comment below the photo!Today's tutorial is the makeup from this photo.This is my daily  makeup for summer.This look is all about light texture and colour :)안녕하세요!
